images.description: SDSS image of region near elliptical galaxy NGC 1129 overlaid on a DSS background to fill in missing areas, also showing NGC 1130, NGC 1131 and IC 265; also shown is PGC 10980, which is sometimes misidentified as NGC 1131
SDSS image of elliptical galaxy NGC 1129, also showing NGC 1130 and NGC 1131
